comments: Kaminsky (CHA) makes incidental hand on ball contact when defending Aldridge's (SAS) shot near the rim.
Williams (CHA) and Gay (SAS) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Kaminsky (CHA) makes contact with Aldridge (SAS) and affects his FOM.
Bridges (CHA) makes marginal contact with Gay (SAS) during the rebound and does not affect his ability to gather the loose ball.
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Bridges (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Forbes (SAS) and Bacon (CHA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
White (SAS) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) during his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
White (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Walker's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Bacon (CHA) and does not deliver contact. The two players briefly engage and separate after the screen.
Kaminsky (CHA) jumps along with DeRozan (SAS) on his path to the basket and does not initiate the contact on the driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Walker (CHA) lifts his pivot foot.
LAR shows DeRozan (SAS) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact while defending Walker's (CHA) driving shot attempt. The contact causes DeRozan's body to turn away from Walker.
Bridges (CHA) makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) arm after he releases his shot attempt and does not affect his ability to follow-through.
Williams (CHA) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
